original: Ahlskog, Bengt Gustaf Edv^ard, tandläkare, Motala, f. 26/6/09 i Tiders-rum, östergötl. 1., av hemmiäg. G. W. Karlsson o. Signe Margareta Eriksson. — Studiex. v. Motala samgymn. 29, tandlikand. 32, tandläkare 35. Assist, i Visby 36, vik. i Härnösand s. å., praktik i Motala sed. 37.
translated: Ahlskog, Bengt Gustaf Edv^ard, dentist, Motala, b. June 26, 1909 in Tiders-rum, östergötl. 1., son of G. W. Karlsson and Signe Margareta Eriksson, who were homeowners. He graduated from Motala samgymnasium in 1929, completed his dental studies in 1932, and became a dentist in 1935. He worked as an assistant in Visby in 1936, as a substitute in Härnösand the same year, and has had his own practice in Motala since 1937.
